---
import { Image } from '@astrojs/image/components'
import Layout from '@/components/Layout.astro'
import Banner from '@/components/Banner.astro'
---

<Layout title="About Us - PURaFOG">
  <Banner title="About Us" />
  <main>
    <section class="lg:px-72 py-16 px-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold capitalize text-gray-600">Who are we?</h2>
        <div class="max-w-5xl flex flex-col gap-6 text-gray-700 text-lg">
          <p>
            Many years ago, we found black mold in our home, like many we thought we could use
            bleach to kill it, little did we know, this only made the situation worse, soon
            thereafter, our children began having respiratory issues and the mold came back, we
            freaked out and contacted a mold remediation company, we were blown away at how
            expensive this process was!
          </p>
          <p>
            Many years passed and I decided to make this more affordable for all! Clean air is so
            important for good health!
          </p>
          <p>
            I am honored to being a female owned company that strives to make your air clean for you
            and your family!
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-12 mt-6">
          <Image
            src="/img/lisa.jpg"
            alt="Lisa - PURaFOG"
            width="100"
            height="100"
            style={{
              borderRadius: '100px 100px 100px 100px',
            }}
          />
          <div>
            <h3
              class="text-5xl text-green-600 font-medium"
              style={{
                fontFamily: 'Great Vibes,sans-serif',
              }}
            >
              Lisa S.
            </h3>
            <span class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700">CEO & Founder of PURaFOG</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-12 lg:py-24">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap flex-col lg:flex-row gap-6 lg:gap-0 justify-between mx-7 lg:mx-48">
        <div class="w-full lg:w-[480px]">
          <Image src="/img/purafog-van.jpg" alt="PURaFOG Van" width="2560" height="1920" />
        </div>
        <div class="mx-auto">
          <Image src="/img/dog-1.jpg" alt="Dog 1" width="360" height="600" />
        </div>
        <div class="mx-auto">
          <Image src="/img/dog-2.jpg" alt="Dog 1" width="360" height="352" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="centered mt-24 mx-6 lg:mx-0">
        <Image src="/img/certificate.png" alt="Dog 1" width="935" height="701" />
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
